* Croatia has an embassy in [[Ankara]] and two consulates-general in [[Istanbul]] and [[İzmir]].
* Turkey has an embassy in [[Zagreb]].
* Both countries are full members of the [[Council of Europe]], [[Union for the Mediterranean]] and [[NATO]]. Both have been [[EU]] [[Future enlargement of the European Union|candidates]] since 2005.
