}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{cite  journal |  last = Drayton | first = Penny| year =  1993  | month = January | title = Aphrodite's island | journal = Wood &amp; water | volume = 2  | issue  = 41}} Cited by: {{cite journal
