* Romania has an embassy in [[Nicosia]] since November 1960.&lt;ref&gt;[http://nicosia.mae.ro/index.php?lang=en   Romanian embassy in Nicosia]&lt;/ref&gt;
* Cyprus has an embassy in [[Bucharest]].
* Cyprus joined the [[European Union]] as a full member on May 1, 2004, while Romania joined on January 1, 2007.
* [http://www.mfa.gov.cy/mfa/mfa2006.nsf/All/9C7139024C6BFFBDC22571E1003AC10E/$file/Romania.pdf?OpenElement  Cyprus Foreign Ministry: list of bilateral treaties between Cyprus and Romania]
