* Mexico is represented in Cyprus through its embassy in [[Athens]] ([[Greece]]) and through an honorary consulate in [[Nicosia]].
* [http://www.mfa.gov.cy/mfa/mfa2006.nsf/All/6829B0ED3F28B048C22571E1002E360F/$file/Mexico.pdf?OpenElement  Cyprus Foreign Affairs: List of bilateral treaties with Mexico]
|--valign=&quot;top&quot;
