      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=July 2010}}
{{Infobox musical artist
| &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians --&gt;
| Name            = Cypress Hill
| Img             = Cypress Hill crop.jpg| Img_capt        = From left to right: [[Sen Dog]], [[Eric Bobo]] and [[B-Real]] on stage during 2006 [[Bonnaroo Music Festival]].
