| Label           = [[Ruffhouse Records|Ruffhouse]]/[[Columbia Records|Columbia]]/[[Sony Music Entertainment|SME Records]]&lt;small&gt;(1990–1999)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;br&gt;Columbia/[[Sony Music Entertainment|SME Records]] &lt;small&gt;(1999–2009)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;br&gt;[[Priority Records|Priority/EMI Records]]
| Associated_acts = [[Psycho Realm]], [[Funkdoobiest]], [[John Frusciante]], [[Tom Morello]], [[Ice Cube]], [[Richie Londres]], [[Snoop Dogg]], [[Xzibit]], [[House of Pain]], [[Pearl Jam]], [[Sonic Youth]], [[Deftones]], [[Young De]], [[MC Breed]], [[Los Lobos]]
