 |unicode=[http://www.unicode.org/charts/PDF/U0400.pdf U+0400&amp;ndash;U+04FF]&lt;br&gt;[http://www.unicode.org/charts/PDF/U0500.pdf U+0500&amp;ndash;U+052F]&lt;br&gt;[http://www.unicode.org/charts/PDF/U2DE0.pdf U+2DE0&amp;ndash;U+2DFF]&lt;br&gt;[http://www.unicode.org/charts/PDF/UA640.pdf U+A640&amp;ndash;U+A69F]
